Package: directCarePlanR
Title: Financial Planning for Direct Care Practice Launches
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Anthony W.", "Raborn", , "anthony@raborndecisionsciences.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Business logic for planning a direct care practice launch.
    Unlike directCareForecastR, which projects forward from a practice's
    actual financial history, this package projects forward from a
    physician's assumptions about a practice that does not yet exist. It
    provides market context lookups, membership and fee revenue
    modeling, multi-scenario financial projections, startup capital and
    runway calculations, and narrative interpretation of the results.
